NKK switches Logo NKK SWITCHES CO., LTD. is a designer and manufacturer of diversified industrial operational switches with FY2010 sales of $96 million. NKK Switches offers illuminated, process sealed, miniature, specialty, surface mount and LCD programmable switches. The company manufactures toggle, rocker, pushbutton, slide, rotary, DIP rotary, keypad and keylock switches. Source
